  <Docs>
    <summary>Specifies the Vulkan component swizzle mapping used for YCbCr color conversion.</summary>
    <remarks><format type="text/markdown"><![CDATA[
## Remarks

`GRVkYcbcrComponents` specifies the Vulkan component swizzle mapping for each color channel (R, G, B, A) used during YCbCr conversion. Each property holds a `VkComponentSwizzle` value that controls how the corresponding channel is sourced from the image data.

This struct maps directly to `VkComponentMapping` in the Vulkan API and is used as part of <xref:SkiaSharp.GRVkYcbcrConversionInfo> when creating a Vulkan YCbCr sampler conversion.
]]></format></remarks>
  </Docs>
